adjust_max_gp
Discworld living help
adjust_max_gp

Name
.SI 5
adjust_max_gp - adjusts the maximun gps.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
void adjust_max_gp(int mgp);
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
This adjusts the maximun gps for the object.  The current guild points
are scaled.  This means if you set the max gps to say 100 from 50
the current gps were 25, when this function had finished the current
gps would be 25.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
query_max_gp, adjust_max_gp, query_gp
.EP
